{"tid":766124,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【火花四濺】泫雅出道11年首拍拖！","createTime":"2018-08-03T10:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T14:16:57.000Z","uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"acd638529e5036ebbe2e652a6fed4a8c09546054","tid":766124,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"韓國性感歌手泫雅，今日（3日）認戀小兩歲的PENTAGON師弟E&rsquo;Dawn，直認感情已發展2年之多，並表示希望在戀情爆出後對粉絲坦白，光明磊落的在舞台上表演，是泫雅出道11年來首次爆拍拖！兩位當事人同屬三人特別企劃組合Triple H，風格大膽煽情，所以過去不論在舞台、MV、節目等場合他們都不忌諱身體接觸，甚有化學反應，想不擦出火花都幾難！<br />\n<br />\n另外，Triple H另一位成員Hui也被爆跟師妹(G)I-DLE成員穗珍拍拖；PENTAGON成員Yuto亦被指跟同門的CLC成員睿恩交住，全部都有相為證，並透過所屬社承認消息，不過就聲明Hui和穗珍已經分手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KqlhhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KqlhhA&d=U5WQoB%2BrW8vOy%2Fuzzd4sKJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=dcc17148\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KqlhhA</a>"},{"pid":"e4f49df74818ba265e27b59e7d6ebb6ba814d876","tid":766124,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"泫雅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0953b40302ca64bc2928b038199945b9e8e2c2a4","tid":766124,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd081c540dd6068059b7890a93a8a86420dcc86","tid":766124,"uid":30924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4f49df74818ba265e27b59e7d6ebb6ba814d876","tid":766124,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"泫雅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"晚晚騎係條仔上面係撚咁搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268abeab66fa6782cd35551becfad